.TH LIBSHA2_BEHEX_UPPER 3 2019-02-09 libsha2
.SH NAME
libsha2_behex_upper \- Convert binary to upper case hexadecimal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
#include <libsha2.h>

void libsha2_behex_upper(char *restrict \fIoutput\fP, const void *restrict \fIhashsum\fP, size_t \fIn\fP);
.fi
.PP
Link with
.IR \-lsha2 .
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.BR libsha2_behex_upper ()
function converts the
.I n
first bytes of
.I hashsum
to upper case hexadecimal, as exactly
.I 2*n
characters, and stores the result, with
NUL byte termination, to
.IR output .
.PP
The user must make sure that
.I output
is at least
.I 2*n+1
bytes large.
